395
00:35:52,520 --> 00:35:56,990
Yeong Seon, waktu berlalu.

396
00:35:56,990 --> 00:36:01,500
Sejujurnya, setiap hari itu meresahkan.

397
00:36:01,500 --> 00:36:08,790
